oon Zandi|Zandi]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Mehdi Mahdavikia|Mahdavikia]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Reza Enayati|Enayati]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Rasoul Khatibi|Khatibi]]}}\n|align=left| [[Vahid Talebloo|Talebloo]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2007-07-22}}\n|-\n| {{nts|16}}.\n| {{fb|IRQ|2004}}\n|align=center| [[2007 AFC Asian Cup knockout stage#Iraq vs South Korea|0\u20130]]\n| {{fb|KOR|1997}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20133'''}}\n|align=center| 0\u20132\n|align=center| 4\u20135\n|align=right| [[Noor Sabri|Sabri]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|[[Hawar Mulla Mohammed|M. Mohammed]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Qusay Munir|Munir]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Haidar Abdul-Amir|Abdul-Amir]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Ahmad Mnajed|Mnajed]] {{pengoal}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|{{pengoal}} [[Lee Chun-soo]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Lee Dong-gook]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Cho Jae-jin]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Yeom Ki-hun]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||#FE8080|{{penmiss}} [[Kim Jung-woo]]}}}}\n|align=left| [[Lee Woon-Jae]]\n|{{Hs|5}} [[2007 AFC Asian Cup#Semifinals|Semi-finals]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2007-07-25}}\n|-\n| {{nts|17}}.\n| {{fb|KOR|1997}}\n|align=center| [[2007 AFC Asian Cup knockout stage#Third place play-off|0\u20130]]\n| {{fb|JPN}}\n| {{CNone|'''6\u20135'''}}\n|align=center| 0\u20131\n|align=center| 6\u20136\n|align=right| [[Lee Woon-Jae]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Cho Jae-jin]] {{pengoal}}}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Oh Beom-seok]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Lee Chun-soo]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Lee Ho (footballer, born 1984)|Lee Ho]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Kim Jin-kyu]] {{pengoal}}}}\n----\n{{nowrap|[[Kim Chi-woo]] {{pengoal}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Shunsuke Nakamura|S. Nak